Help on command: FRIENDS

  Usage       : friends [ list | add (arg) | remove (arg) ]
  Description : Friends command is an adequate succour to see the list
                of your friends currently playing. The size of your list
                is currently limited to 40. Using this command without an
                argument will list all of your friends currenlty logged in.

  Examples    : friends add cendor
                friends remove cendor
                friends list (Character '*' indicates that the character is
                              currently logged in)
